\c 20
\s Imizi yokuphephela
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuJoshuwa isithi:
\v 2 Khuluma kubantwana bakoIsrayeli uthi: Zikhetheleni imizi yokuphephela\x + Eks. 21.13. Nani 35.6,11,14. Dute. 19.2,3,4,5,6.\x* engakhuluma ngayo kini ngesandla sikaMozisi,
\v 3 ukuze umbulali obulala umuntu kungeyisikho ngabomo\x + 20.9. Nani 35.11.\x* engazi\x + 20.5.\x* abalekele khona. Njalo izakuba yisiphephelo kini kumphindiseli wegazi.
\v 4 Nxa ebalekela komunye walimizi uzakuma emnyango wesango lomuzi\x + Ruthe 4.1,2.\x*, akhulume udaba lwakhe ezindlebeni zabadala balowomuzi; babesebememukela kubo emzini, bamnike indawo ukuthi ahlale labo.
\v 5 Uba-ke umphindiseli wegazi exotshana laye, kabayikunikela\x + Dute. 32.30.\x* umbulali esandleni sakhe, ngoba utshaye umakhelwane wakhe engazi\x + 20.3. Dute. 4.42; 19.4.\x*, ebengamzondi mandulo.
\v 6 Uzahlala kulowomuzi aze eme phambi kwenhlangano kusenzelwa ukwahlulelwa\x + 20.9. Nani 35.12,24.\x*, kuze kube lokufa kompristi omkhulu\x + Nani 35.25.\x* oyabe ekhona ngalezonsuku. Umbulali usengabuyela eze emzini wakibo lendlini yakhe, aye emzini abaleke khona.
\p
\v 7 Basebengcwelisa iKedeshi\x + 19.37.\x* eGalili entabeni yakoNafithali, leShekema\x + 17.7.\x* entabeni yakoEfrayimi\x + 24.33.\x*, leKiriyathi-Arba\x + 21.11. Luka 1.39.\x* okuyiHebroni entabeni yakoJuda.
\v 8 Langaphetsheya kweJordani eJeriko empumalanga banika iBezeri\x + Dute. 4.43. Josh. 21.36. 1 Lan. 6.78.\x* enkangala emagcekeni\x + Dute. 3.10.\x* esizweni sakoRubeni, leRamothi eGileyadi esizweni sakoGadi\x + 21.38. 1 Kho. 22.3.\x*, leGolani eBashani esizweni sakoManase\x + Dute. 4.43. Josh. 21.27. 1 Lan. 6.71.\x*.
\v 9 Le yimizi eyayimiselwe bonke abantwana bakoIsrayeli lowezizwe ohlala njengowezizwe phakathi kwabo\x + Nani 35.15.\x*, ukuze loba ngubani obulala umuntu kungeyisikho ngabomo abalekele khona\x + 20.3.\x*, ukuze angafi ngesandla somphindiseli wegazi, aze eme phambi kwenhlangano\x + 20.6.\x*.